{"tid":1007951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地足球] 2018/19 港超聯及香港隊討論區 (69)","createTime":"2019-02-04T06:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T09:30:05.000Z","uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc4fed2939494369aac96ddf7c93bae1750236f","tid":1007951,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOwHc14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOwHc14.jpg&h=e62a15f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018/19 港超參賽球隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志</span>、<span style=\"color: green;\">和富大埔</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港飛馬</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">東方</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">XX南區</span>、<span style=\"color: orange;\">佳聯元朗</span>、<del>畜力R&amp;F</del>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">理</span>文、<span style=\"color: violet;\">夢想FC</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">凱</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">景</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2019亞冠外圍賽第二圈參賽資格 - 傑志</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">2019亞協附加賽參賽資格 - 和富大埔</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em><span style=\"color: red;\">傑志如亞冠外出局，將轉戰亞協分組賽；如晉級亞冠分組賽，將由香港飛馬出戰亞協分組賽</span></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/football_20181122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Ffootball_20181122.jpg&h=b4573605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">賀歲盃 2019</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/affDVgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaffDVgH.jpg&h=3df4bfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkfa.com/upload/20182019/Lunar New Year Cup/Lunar New Year Cup 2019 V.3(resize).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfa.com%2Fupload%2F20182019%2FLunar%20New%20Year%20Cup%2FLunar%20New%20Year%20Cup%202019%20V.3%28resize%29.jpg&h=ea3eed93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2020亞洲足協U-23錦標賽外圍賽</strong></span></span><br />\nG組球隊<br />\n🇭🇰香港、🇰🇵北韓、🇸🇬新加坡、🇲🇳蒙古<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小組首名及四支最佳次名球隊晉級決賽週</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>賽程 (G組賽事由蒙古主辦)</ins><br />\n<br />\n2019年3月22日<br />\n🇰🇵北韓 vs 🇲🇳蒙古<br />\n🇭🇰香港 vs 🇸🇬新加坡<br />\n<br />\n2019年3月24日<br />\n🇲🇳蒙古 vs 🇭🇰香港<br />\n🇸🇬新加坡 vs 🇰🇵北韓<br />\n<br />\n2019年3月26日<br />\n🇰🇵北韓 vs 🇭🇰香港<br />\n🇸🇬新加坡 vs 🇲🇳蒙古<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"186eabf7cdf7fd89496ac83344f3ffd95133fc52","tid":1007951,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第41屆省港盃冠軍 香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxErCiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxErCiL.jpg&h=ca9ace6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>23人名單</strong></span></ins><br />\n守門員<br />\n謝家榮 (<span style=\"color: violet;\">夢想FC</span>)、高俊 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">理</span>文)、蔡子濤 (<span style=\"color: red;\">冠忠南區</span>)<br />\n<br />\n後衛<br />\n鍾昇霖 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">標準流浪</span>)、潘栢安 (<span style=\"color: violet;\">夢想FC</span>)、陳靜謙 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">東方龍獅</span>)、羅梓駿 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志</span>)、余煒廉 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">理</span>文)、梁諾恆 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">富力R&amp;F</span>)<br />\n<br />\n中場<br />\n茹子楠 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">東方龍獅</span>)、何振廷 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">凱</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">景</span>)、胡晉銘 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港飛馬</span>)、鄭展龍 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志</span>)、杜國榆 (聖文德大學)<br />\n<br />\n前鋒<br />\n陳廣豪 (<span style=\"color: orange;\">佳聯元朗</span>)、林樂勤 、彭林林 (<span style=\"color: violet;\">夢想FC</span>)、播磨浩謙、孫銘謙 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">凱</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">景</span>)、鄭兆均 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">理</span>文)、袁振昇 (<span style=\"color: blue;\">富力R&amp;F</span>)、鄭子森 (<span style=\"color: green;\">和富大埔</span>)、安永佳 (三藩市大學)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">首回合</span></strong></ins><br />\n2019年1月6日 (<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>廣東省人民體育場</strong></span>)<br />\n中國廣東 2-1 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">入球球員:</span></strong> <strong> 林樂勤</strong> 90' (<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">夢想FC</span></strong>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rxm9z89.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxm9z89.gif&h=1124b2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykqa32v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fykqa32v.gif&h=56e6d173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>次回合</span></strong></ins><br />\n2019年1月9日 (<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>香港大球場</strong></span>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span></strong> 4-0 中國廣東<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">入球球員:</span></strong> <strong> 安永佳</strong> 22' (<strong>Syracuse University</strong>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUYDtqr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUYDtqr.gif&h=22a220e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeJv3YP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeJv3YP.gif&h=1d232186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4r9z5w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4r9z5w.gif&h=d02cfdf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">入球球員:</span></strong> <strong> 梁諾恆</strong> 50' (<strong